    <gsw_content_information action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE">
        <active>true</active>
        <article><![CDATA[<p>Set the &#34;x_taniu_tan_core.all_computers_action_group_id&#34; System Property to the <strong>ID</strong> of the <strong>Default - All Computers</strong> Action Group (<em>not to be confused with Computer Groups</em>).<br />To find this ID in Tanium, navigate to <strong>Administration</strong> &gt; <strong>Actions</strong> &gt; <strong>Action Groups</strong>. Click the three vertical lines at the top-right of the list and make sure that the <strong>ID</strong> column is checked. Find the group called &#34;Default - All Computers&#34;, and grab the value from the ID column and copy it into this property.</p>]]></article>
